scenes.description: Opening title card for 'Neverland Paradox' featuring Ninomae Ina'nis.
Ninomae Ina'nis performs the song 'wonderland' on a stylized 3D stage set in a forest at night.

subtitles.english: wonderland

subtitles.original: 迷い込んだ森にある本当
